{
  "id": null,
  "title": "SRE Dashboard - Production Architecture",
  "tags": ["sre", "slo", "production"],
  "style": "dark",
  "timezone": "browser", 
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-1h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "API Services Availability (Internal)",
      "type": "stat",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "((sum(rate(http_requests_total{service=\"backend-service\",status_code!~\"5..\"}[5m])) or vector(0)) / (sum(rate(http_requests_total{service=\"backend-service\"}[5m])) or vector(1))) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "Backend API",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "((sum(rate(http_requests_total{service=\"ai-service\",status!~\"5..\"}[5m])) or vector(0)) / (sum(rate(http_requests_total{service=\"ai-service\"}[5m])) or vector(1))) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "AI Service API",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 95,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {"color": "red", "value": 99},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 99.5},
              {"color": "green", "value": 99.9}
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0}
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "External Frontend Monitoring (User-Facing)",
      "type": "stat",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "probe_success{instance=\"https://todo-app.natsuki-cloud.dev\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Frontend Available",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "probe_duration_seconds{instance=\"https://todo-app.natsuki-cloud.dev\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Page Load Time",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {"options": {"0": {"text": "❌ DOWN"}}, "type": "value"},
            {"options": {"1": {"text": "✅ UP"}}, "type": "value"}
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {"color": "red", "value": 0},
              {"color": "green", "value": 1}
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Page Load Time"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "unit", "value": "s"},
              {"id": "mappings", "value": []},
              {"id": "thresholds", "value": {
                "steps": [
                  {"color": "green", "value": 0},
                  {"color": "yellow", "value": 1},
                  {"color": "red", "value": 3}
                ]
              }}
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0}
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "API Traffic Rate (Backend Services)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(http_requests_total{service=\"backend-service\"}[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "Backend - {{method}} {{status_code}}",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "rate(http_requests_total{service=\"ai-service\"}[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "AI Service - {{method}} {{status}}",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10
          }
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 6}
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "User-Facing Response Times",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "probe_duration_seconds{instance=\"https://todo-app.natsuki-cloud.dev\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Frontend (via CloudFront)",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=\"backend-service\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Backend API p95",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=\"ai-service\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "AI Service API p95",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": 0},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 1},
              {"color": "red", "value": 3}
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 6}
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "SLO Targets vs Current Performance",
      "type": "table",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "probe_success{job=\"blackbox-external-targets\"}",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "refId": "A",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "__name__": true,
              "Time": true,
              "job": true
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "instance": "Service Endpoint",
              "Value": "Status (1=UP, 0=DOWN)"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "displayMode": "table"
          },
          "mappings": [
            {"options": {"0": {"text": "❌ DOWN", "color": "red"}}, "type": "value"},
            {"options": {"1": {"text": "✅ UP", "color": "green"}}, "type": "value"}
          ]
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 14}
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Architecture Note",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 14},
      "options": {
        "content": "## Production Architecture\n\n**Frontend**: React SPA served via CloudFront CDN\n- External monitoring via Blackbox Exporter\n- Most requests served by CloudFront edge cache\n- Origin (nginx) sees minimal traffic\n\n**Backend APIs**: Direct container monitoring\n- Internal Prometheus instrumentation\n- Real request/response metrics\n\n**SLO Targets**:\n- Frontend: <2s page load, 99.9% availability\n- Backend: <200ms API, 99.95% availability  \n- AI Service: <2s processing, 99.5% availability"
      }
    }
  ]
}